<div class="comment-content">
<p>I don&#8217;t get the point of using the microwave in the first place.  How difficult is it to pop the corn in a saucepan with a few drops of oil?  That eliminates the need to kill trees to make the paper bag.  Plus, neither you nor your popcorn will glow in the dark.</p>
<cite>&#8212; Robert Rothman</cite>
</div>
</li>
