<div class="comment-content">
<p>Hurrah!  I&#8217;ve only been subject to the noxious smell of microwave popcorn; mercifully not the taste.  Three cheers for ridding the planet of that horror.  Consumption nightmare aside, there is a serious risk to people who work with microwave popcorn.  The fumes from the butter flavoring are very dangerous.  Yellow-lung disease?</p>
<cite>&#8212; Brenda</cite>
</div>
