<p>This is great! Even the &#8220;light&#8221; versions of microwave popborn have stuff that turns the kernals a lighter shade of Cheato orange. <a href="http://www.oatmealcookie.typepad.com" rel="nofollow">http://www.oatmealcookie.typepad.com</a></p>
