</div>
<div class="comment-content">
<p>I make popcorn almost every night using a &#8220;Whirlypop&#8221;. It&#8217;s a stovetop popper that requires very little oil and makes perfect popcorn in about 2 minutes.</p>
<p>I teach at a well-known culinary school and have had students who didn&#8217;t know there was any other way to make popcorn but in a microwave! They are shocked when I tell them otherwise&#8230;</p>
<cite>&#8212; chefsmartypants</cite>
