</div><div class="box module"><h4>About Diner&#039;s Journal</h4><div class="entry">
<p class="summary">Diner’s Journal embraces news and opinion about recipes, wine, restaurants and other matters culinary. Contributors include <a href="/author/eric-asimov">Eric Asimov</a>, <a href="/author/glenn-collins">Glenn Collins</a>, <a href="/author/florence-fabricant">Florence Fabricant</a>, <a href="/author/nick-fox">Nick Fox</a>, <a href="/author/jeff-gordinier">Jeff Gordinier</a>, <a href="/author/elaine-louie">Elaine Louie</a>, <a href="/author/julia-moskin">Julia Moskin</a>, <a href="/author/sam-sifton">Sam Sifton</a>, <a href="/author/samantha-storey">Samantha Storey</a>, <a href="/author/emily-weinstein">Emily Weinstein</a>, <a href="/author/pete-wells">Pete Wells</a> and others.</p>
<ul class="refer">
<li><a href="http://www.facebook.com/nytimesdining">Check us out on Facebook »</a></li>
<li><a href="http://twitter.com/nytimesdining">Follow us on Twitter »</a></li>
<li><a href="mailto:dinejournal@nytimes.com">E-mail us with tips and suggestions. »</a></li>
<li><a href="/feed">Subscribe to our feed »</a></li>
</ul>
